{
  "stem": "13483.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only know I'm Jewish because I'm Jewish, but as far as him up there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How else could you feel?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you think, how could people-- you know, how could they do a thing like that?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Especially also knowing, I suppose, because you know it wasn't only Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It some of their own people, you know, they did it to, lots of German, non-Jewish people were put into these camps as well just because they didn't side with the Nazi philosophy, you know, or they were socialists or they were communists or they were gypsies.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where, in Germany?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we heard quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think a lot of it did happen, not-- maybe not necessarily in Germany, but in places like Czechoslovakia and France where they had massacres-- massacred.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a place called Oradour-sur-Glane where the Germans [INAUDIBLE] executed a whole village and also like in Czechoslovakia in Lidice where they slaughtered a whole village, so you heard about these things.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met American soldiers, and I met Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't see many French soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were mainly Maquis-- the Maquis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, I met Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I met American soldiers and then French soldiers I didn't meet, [LAUGHS] very strange.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Allied prison of war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't recollect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recollect.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything I recollect, they weren't Allied, but German slave workers who were being shipped back to their own countries, I saw that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I don't know, but I should think like France, Germany-- France, Poland, Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They love Russian slave workers that we knew about, Polish slave workers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I went to-- we went on to Magdeburg-- was it Magdeburg?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
